Task:
OSA detection (binary at AHI≥5/15/30); 
OSA severity classification (4-class); 
Sleep stage classification (3-class: Wake/NREM/REM)

Performance:
MobileNet V1: 89.5% accuracy; 
MobileNet V1 + LSTM: 90% accuracy; 
MobileNet V1 + GRU: 90.29% accuracy

Feature / Input:
Speech (audio: cough, breathing, vowel, counting)
Spectral features; Cepstral features (MFCC, GTCC); Spectral descriptors; 
Periodicity features; 5701-dim statistical feature vector
